name: Friday Night Funkin' vs Sans | FNF Mod | HTML 5 Online Port
name_original: Friday Night Funkin' vs Sans | FNF Mod | HTML 5 Online Port
description:
Friday Night Funkin' vs Sans is a fan-made crossover mod for the music rhythm game Friday Night Funkin'. The mod features Sans the skeleton from Undertale and three new songs.

The downloadable version of the mod, on which this port is based, is available here. All the credit goes to fuzzehead06.
